'''Channel 81''' was a [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] channel designated for diplomatic uses. Messages were sent to and from diplomatic missions, embassies, home governments and [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] offices. On one occasion, a [[Yevetha]]n [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] broadcast for propaganda appeared on the channel, where the [[Grand Imperial Union]] declared support for the [[Duskhan League]] in its war against the New Republic.

